        <briefdescription>
<para>Send a message to the platform. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Used to send a message to the platform over a given TX channel.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>the transport driver is in no way allowed to overwrite the value of the <computeroutput>use_polling</computeroutput> parameter and must comply with it.</para>
</simplesect>
